    "description": "AudioTheory Piano Keys 是学习或练习钢琴的终极互动学习工具。它采用创新的彩色编码系统和可定制的和弦与音阶图，高亮显示你弹奏的每个音符，帮助你直观理解乐理基础。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513510/extras/a8a21b9219a3cc0edb00ade656a7cee9.poster.avif?t=1770909701\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513510/extras/a8a21b9219a3cc0edb00ade656a7cee9.webm?t=1770909701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513510/extras/a8a21b9219a3cc0edb00ade656a7cee9.mp4?t=1770909701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AudioTheory Piano Keys 的功能</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>创新的高亮系统</strong> 让你快速了解所弹奏的音符如何与和弦和音阶相匹配。<br></li><li><strong>完全支持 MIDI 输入。</strong> 连接外部 MIDI 输入设备，即可控制屏幕键盘。支持实时音频反馈和可视化高亮显示，并提供多种软件乐器预设。<br></li><li><strong>排除音符</strong> 再也不会偏离调性。从丰富的音阶库中快速加载所需音阶。<br></li><li><strong>选择作曲所需的和弦</strong> 从丰富的和弦库中选择，或自动显示与所选音阶预设对应的和弦。<br></li><li><strong>自定义视图</strong> 键盘尺寸可从 37 键调节至完整的 88 键钢琴。<br></li><li><strong>全新推出音阶轮。</strong> AudioTheory Piano Keys 的全新功能。所选音阶将在圆形图示中高亮显示，帮助你清晰直观地理解音阶相对于根音的结构关系。<br></li><li><strong>练耳练习</strong> 帮助你通过听觉理解并识别音乐。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513510/extras/8b52e2f8e8176e47cc18bf8e21765ed6.poster.avif?t=1770909701\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513510/extras/8b52e2f8e8176e47cc18bf8e21765ed6.webm?t=1770909701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513510/extras/8b52e2f8e8176e47cc18bf8e21765ed6.mp4?t=1770909701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>此外，还有一项全新功能，将改变你直观理解乐理的方式…<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >实时音阶高亮</h2><br>主界面上方设有第二排键盘，用于显示当前演奏音符对应的音阶。这意味着你不仅可以查看乐曲的主音阶（加载在键盘上），还可以看到根据当前根音筛选出的音符。它是即兴演奏的理想工具，能帮助你在演奏过程中快速识别合适的音符。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513510/extras/364e5f98304ddcf944e385ab90d5f265.poster.avif?t=1770909701\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513510/extras/364e5f98304ddcf944e385ab90d5f265.webm?t=1770909701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513510/extras/364e5f98304ddcf944e385ab90d5f265.mp4?t=1770909701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
